## Testing Policies

```sql
-- Test as full-access role
USE ROLE AUTOMATED_INTELLIGENCE;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM RAW.CUSTOMERS;  -- All rows

-- Test as restricted role
USE ROLE WEST_COAST_MANAGER;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM RAW.CUSTOMERS;  -- Only CA, OR, WA rows

-- Verify the policy is attached
SELECT * FROM TABLE(INFORMATION_SCHEMA.POLICY_REFERENCES(
  REF_ENTITY_NAME => 'AUTOMATED_INTELLIGENCE.RAW.CUSTOMERS',
  REF_ENTITY_DOMAIN => 'TABLE'
));
```
